class Solution:
    def maxChunksToSorted(self, arr):
        """
        :type arr: List[int]
        :rtype: int
        """
        
        i = j = k = 0
        
        while(i < len(arr)):
            if arr[i] == 0:
                i += 1
            else:
                j = i + 1
                
                while(j < len(arr) and arr[j] > 0):
                    j += 1
                    
                if j - i >= 2:
                    k += 1
                    i = j
            
        return k
